  "messages": [
   {
    "with": "Priya Venkataraman",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just skimmed a recruiter InMail about a Principal Platform role – feels like a copy‑paste from a template. No real numbers, just buzzwords. Thought you’d want a heads‑up before they hit you.",
    "time": "2026-05-04T20:49:05"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "They pinged back with a one‑liner “Thanks for your interest, let’s chat.” No depth, no equity hints. Same old silent‑treatment game. Frustrating as usual.",
    "time": "2026-05-05T20:48:42"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus Yeoh",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Got a second InMail – they finally mentioned “competitive compensation” but still vague on vesting. Do you think it’s worth a call, or should I keep it on the back‑burner?",
    "time": "2026-05-07T20:53:40"
   },
   {
    "with": "Arjun Deshpande",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Left a voicemail for the recruiter; they’ll call back next week. I’m leaning to schedule, but need to see the full package first – especially the IVF coverage and loan‑clearance bits.",
    "time": "2026-05-08T20:51:32"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Looks like they finally dropped a concrete figure: $300K base + $400K equity. That matches the floor we talked about. If you’re comfortable, this could be the “reasonable offer” you mentioned.",
    "time": "2026-05-10T20:01:40"
   },
   {
    "with": "Priya Venkataraman",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just got a generic recruiter InMail about a “Principal Platform” role. The language feels recycled—no mention of my multi‑region failover work. Thought you’d want to see the tone before I waste any more energy.",
    "time": "2026-05-11T20:51:51"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Forwarded the recruiter’s follow‑up. They’re pushing a base of $260K and a vague equity teaser. I’m leaning on you to sanity‑check the numbers before I reply.",
    "time": "2026-05-12T20:18:22"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Quick dive: the comp band they quoted sits at $260‑$280K base, 0.5‑0.7 M equity over four years. That’s below my floor of $285K base + $400K equity. Any thoughts on framing a counter?",
    "time": "2026-05-13T15:31:44"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just got a Signal SMS from the same recruiter—“Can we hop on a call tomorrow?” I’m wary they’re trying to pressure me. Should I ghost or set a hard deadline?",
    "time": "2026-05-13T21:05:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "Priya Venkataraman",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "They finally added equity details: 120k RSUs vesting over 4 yr, current price $12. Still underwater. I’m trying to gauge if the signing bonus they hinted at could offset my loan load.",
    "time": "2026-05-15T20:03:51"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "New offer landed: $275K base, $600K equity, plus a $30K signing bonus. The equity is in a pre‑IPO stock, but the vesting cliff is 1 yr. How does this stack against the market for my skill set?",
    "time": "2026-05-16T14:58:06"
   },
   {
    "with": "Arjun Deshpande",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Missed the recruiter’s call; left a voicemail. I told them I’ll need a written offer before any decision. Let’s review the numbers tonight—especially the bonus, since IVF costs are still looming.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T20:02:41"
   },
   {
    "with": "Priya Venkataraman",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Recruiter just texted a $45K signing‑bonus figure. It’s tempting, but I’m still uneasy about the vesting schedule. Do you think it’s enough to offset the RSU dip?",
    "time": "2026-05-17T20:12:50"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I asked the recruiter for a formal offer letter with full grant math. If they comply, I’ll compare it side‑by‑side with our spreadsheet. Keep your eyes peeled for any hidden clauses.",
    "time": "2026-05-17T21:38:45"
   },
   {
    "with": "Alex (Recruiter)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Thanks for reaching out, Alex. Could you send the full equity‑grant model (share count, vesting schedule, price assumptions)? I need to compare it against my current RSU exposure.",
    "time": "2026-05-25T21:38:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "Alex (Recruiter)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Also, what's the remote‑work policy? Fully remote is essential given my IVF schedule and the time‑zone overlap with family in India.",
    "time": "2026-05-26T21:28:32"
   },
   {
    "with": "Priya Venkataraman",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Hey Priya, quick ping—how's the LumenTrace launch? Got a few minutes to chat tomorrow? Need a sanity check on that principal role you mentioned.",
    "time": "2026-05-26T22:33:57"
   },
   {
    "with": "Arjun Deshpande",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Feeling pretty nauseous after the meds. Going to rest on the couch. Might be a rough afternoon.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T16:32:48"
   },
   {
    "with": "Alex (Recruiter)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Got the interview slot at 10 am tomorrow, but I have a medical appointment at 9:30. Could we push it to after 11 am or pick a later slot? Thanks.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T19:47:17"
   },
   {
    "with": "Priya Venkataraman",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Out of office for the next few hours (IVF cycle). Will circle back later today.",
    "time": "2026-05-28T16:27:10"
   },
   {
    "with": "Alex (Recruiter)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "I'm still interested. Could you break down the signing‑bonus (cash vs. restricted stock) and any performance clawbacks? Need to see if it clears the $300K base floor I'm targeting.",
    "time": "2026-05-28T21:02:08"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel Reiss (Blind/Signal)",
    "direction": "outgoing",
